These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, documentary, horror, adventure
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, van, boat
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person driving the van##2
6. the person watching adventure movies is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel     | horror | documentary |
| Transport     | skateboard     | van | boat  | train      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, reggae, salsa, country
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, airplane, subway
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | reggae    | country     | salsa  |
| Transport     | bike    | airplane | jet-ski | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, hip-hop, classical, soul
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, hamster, bird
1. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the fan of soul##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | classical   | metal  | soul |
| Pet           | pony | bird | hamster | chinchilla  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, traveling, cooking, hiking
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, thai, malaysian, mexican
1. the mexican is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is chess and the malaysian##2
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
4. the malaysian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the pakistani is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess | hiking | cooking  |
| Nationality   | thai  | pakistani   | mexican  | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, coffee, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, rock-climbing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | milk    | cola   | coffee | sprite    |
| Hobby      | fishing | board-games | rock-climbing       | video-games |

