.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, sprite, 7up
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, van, ship
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person driving the ship and the person drinking sprite##2
3. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the van and the person drinking cola##2
4. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | cola | sprite | 7up | hot-chocolate |
| Transport   | quad-bike | helicopter  | van    | ship  |

