4. the german is between the brazilian and the italian##2
5. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1
6. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the taxi and the italian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | italian | german | brazilian     |
| Transport     | boat | tram  | roller   | taxi |

