4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
