.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, pony, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, rugby, badminton
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | bird | goldfish   | pony      | rat      |
| Sport   | swimming     | rugby | climbing | badminton |

