There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, turkish, german, australian
1. the mexican is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the fan of dubstep is between the australian and the turkish##2
3. the fan of techno is the turkish##1
4. the german is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the mexican##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | soul | techno | dubstep      | ambient   |
| Nationality   | german  | turkish    | mexican | australian |

