.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, japanese, chinese, australian
4 different pets are kept: dog, snake, rabbit, goldfish
1. the japanese is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is the pakistani##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the chinese is on the left or right of the australian##3
6. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the australian##3
7. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | chinese  | australian | japanese |
| Pet           | rabbit     | goldfish | dog    | snake     |

