.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, cucumber, broccoli, cauliflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, dancer, social-worker, police-officer
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the dancer is on the right of the social-worker##1
3. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the videographer##1
4. the dancer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating broccoli is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | cucumber  | kiwi | cauliflower  | broccoli      |
| Job    | police-officer | videographer | social-worker | dancer |

