5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
6. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
7. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | writing | singing | reading | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | pop       | d&b   | country      |

