3. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
4. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
5. the fan of techno is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
