.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, hot-chocolate, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, swimming
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up     | coffee     | hot-chocolate          | water |
| Sport      | biathlon | lacrosse | swimming | soccer  |

 